{"tid":2220653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要林鄭「講人話」 香港電台記者遭打壓","createTime":"2020-09-27T21:53:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T03:04:13.000Z","uid":337052,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"6f4432e09d1bc4036e7ad3ad758e17ba487c4d2e","tid":2220653,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T21:53:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">要林鄭「講人話」 香港電台記者遭打壓</span></strong><br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/09/28/201.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F09%2F28%2F201.jpg&h=fa9edd12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴基斯坦裔的香港電台記者利君雅，曾多次對港府官員和建制派政治人物尖銳提問，疑似因此遭當局打壓，工作權恐不保。（取自網路）<br />\n<br />\n2020/09/28 05:30<br />\n〔編譯茅毅／綜合報導〕<span class=\"red\">去年香港「反送中」運動期間，曾在香港特首林鄭月娥舉行記者會時，公開要求她「講人話」的公營「香港電台」巴基斯坦裔記者利君雅（Nabela Qoser），據傳在該電台所屬的港府「商務及經濟發展局」施壓下，試用期被延長一百二十天。期間一旦被裁定違反任何守則，就會遭到立即中止合約的命運。香港電台節目製作人員工會質疑，延長試用期「極不尋常」，疑似「無理打壓」記者。</span><br />\n<br />\n該工會證實，二○一七年十月三日到職的利君雅，在長達三年的試用期即將屆滿前，收到台方通知，要求她在二十九日下午五點前，答覆是否接受試用期延長，還提到將針對她在去年七至十一月期間採訪港府記者會時的言行「重啟調查」。<br />\n<br />\n利君雅是在香港生長的港籍巴裔人士，在轉職香港電台前為香港《明報》記者。去年到今年初，她屢屢對林鄭等港府高官與建制派政治人物犀利提問，引發網友熱議，認為「大快人心」。例如，利君雅在林鄭對記者提問避重就輕時，直言要林鄭「正面回答問題」、麻煩「講人話」，還問出席記者會的港府高官「晚上睡不睡得著？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/paper/1402587\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fpaper%2F1402587&d=4SaXJ4tauImRU00LhBBHUphbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=87aabfc4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fpaper%2F1402587&h=f2a927e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/paper/1402587</a>"},{"pid":"f2728506a9ec731d637bdba6c525b3deb212a09a","tid":2220653,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T21:55:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99c93a23d677ebf198425f3de51d0f09dec0013a","tid":2220653,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2728506a9ec731d637bdba6c525b3deb212a09a","tid":2220653,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T21:55:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T21:57:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ebf8df6cf8f10624cac1c9b76a1c6d6738014b","tid":2220653,"uid":337052,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T22:02:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">【極不尋常】港台重啟調查出席記招表現 延長120日試用期 利君雅：我會繼續努力</span></strong><br />\n撰文: 記者張凱傑 | 發佈日期: 27.09.20 | 最後更新: | 2020-09-27 17:41:51<br />\n<br />\n眾新聞獲悉，利君雅遭港台要求延長試用期120日，管方將重啟（reopen）調查利君雅在去年7月至11月期間的投訴，包括出席政府記者會的表現和行為。利君雅需在下周二前回覆管方是否接受延長試用期。眾新聞向利君雅查詢，她只說「多謝關心，我會繼續努力，請大家繼續支持港台。」<br />\n<br />\n去年7月21日元朗發生白衣人無差別施襲事件，行政長官林鄭月娥事隔十多小時後，才率領官員公開見記者。參與記者會的利君雅質疑是否「官、警、黑合演的大龍鳳」，指出在文明社會無差別襲擊已是「恐怖襲擊」，又促林鄭「講人話」，事後獲網民封為「良心記者」、「新聞女神」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2019/07/%E5%88%A9%E5%90%9B%E9%9B%85-%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E6%89%93%E4%BA%BA-20190722235115_2635_large.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2019%2F07%2F%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%2590%259B%25E9%259B%2585-%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2589%2593%25E4%25BA%25BA-20190722235115_2635_large.png&h=f9cf0ccd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n資料圖片<br />\n據了解，一般公務員合約試用期長達三年，利君雅在2017年入職港台，今年即將完成試用期，同期員工亦順利通過程序。據悉，如果利君雅不接受管方延長試用期，意味她在原有試用期完結後，將不獲續聘，需離開港台。<br />\n<br />\n香港電台節目製作人員工會證實收到消息，將會向管方求證了解詳情，質疑「重啟調查」是誰人的決定，亦意味調查原先已經結束，「重啟調查」有何依據？工會亦指出，員工升遷一直以評核報告為依據，是次延長試用期是很罕見、極不尋常、更是無理打壓。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，利君雅最近放大假，有同事見到她上周突然返回公司，相信就是當日收到管方通知。至於新上任的港台顧問委員會主席林大輝將於周一早上到港台開會。<br />\n<br />\n值得留意的是，港台去年多個節目橫掃國際獎項，其中<span class=\"red\">利君雅有份主持的《視點31》，節目《中國大數據生活系列》榮獲美國國際電影及電視節2020「紀錄片：新聞特輯」類別金獎、2020紐約電視電影節「特別報道」類別銅獎、第24屆人權新聞獎紀錄片優異獎。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/34282/%E5%88%A9%E5%90%9B%E9%9B%85-%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%B0%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE%E8%A3%BD%E4%BD%9C%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E6%9C%83-%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%B0-34282/%E3%80%90%E6%A5%B5%E4%B8%8D%E5%B0%8B%E5%B8%B8%E3%80%91%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%B0%E9%87%8D%E5%95%9F%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E8%A8%98%E6%8B%9B%E8%A1%A8%E7%8F%BE-%E5%BB%B6%E9%95%B7120%E6%97%A5%E8%A9%A6%E7%94%A8%E6%9C%9F-%E5%88%A9%E5%90%9B%E9%9B%85%EF%BC%9A%E6%88%91%E6%9C%83%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E5%8A%AA%E5%8A%9B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F34282%2F%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%2590%259B%25E9%259B%2585-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%25AF%2580%25E7%259B%25AE%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E4%25BD%259C%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%259C%2583-%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258F%25B0-34282%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25B0%258B%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258F%25B0%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%2595%259F%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E8%25A8%2598%25E6%258B%259B%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E7%258F%25BE-%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E9%2595%25B7120%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%259C%259F-%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%2590%259B%25E9%259B%2585%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%2588%2591%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%25B9%25BC%25E7%25BA%258C%25E5%258A%25AA%25E5%258A%259B&d=4SaXJ4tauImRU00LhBBHUphbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=16600936\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/34282/%E5%88%A9%E5%90%9B%E9%9B%85-%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%B0%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE%E8%A3%BD%E4%BD%9C%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E6%9C%83-%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%B0-34282/%E3%80%90%E6%A5%B5%E4%B8%8D%E5%B0%8B%E5%B8%B8%E3%80%91%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%B0%E9%87%8D%E5%95%9F%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E8%A8%98%E6%8B%9B%E8%A1%A8%E7%8F%BE-%E5%BB%B6%E9%95%B7120%E6%97%A5%E8%A9%A6%E7%94%A8%E6%9C%9F-%E5%88%A9%E5%90%9B%E9%9B%85%EF%BC%9A%E6%88%91%E6%9C%83%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E5%8A%AA%E5%8A%9B</a>"},{"pid":"287cd8b7d56125373398fcaf2d3d952712e84c6b","tid":2220653,"uid":337052,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T22:12:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wLh2ZgB0lYw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwLh2ZgB0lYw&d=4SaXJ4tauImRU00LhBBHUphbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=1f22df4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wLh2ZgB0lYw</a><br />\n怒嗆林鄭月娥&quot;講人話&quot; 香港新聞女戰神被網友封&quot;良心記者&quot;"},{"pid":"d5a019b6744bf4a4ccbf946361d9cc97c403f86e","tid":2220653,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T22:18:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7SHpKPW8BXs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7SHpKPW8BXs&d=4SaXJ4tauImRU00LhBBHUphbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=cf7c1455\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7SHpKPW8BXs</a><br />\n14-08-2013 | 利君雅 | 機場現場:大量旅客滯留機場"},{"pid":"1bc661510a6fc8e7a31118b7acf75171d3d99e5f","tid":2220653,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T22:34:09.000Z","msg":"香港在中共統治下<br />\n人命只是中共的棋子<br />\n<br />\n香港人命值錢嗎？<br />\n妳的生命隨時可以消失在政府控制的暗巷裡"},{"pid":"9c753840294fe6e0a4ecd46782d2e9d42769ecb7","tid":2220653,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T22:35:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"67634579ed6669743e567ce8f13665a85fb32adb","tid":2220653,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T22:51:51.000Z","msg":"香港電台助理節目主任及主持<br />\n利君雅<br />\nNabela Qoser<br />\n基本資料<br />\n別名 新聞女神、良心記者[1]、真香港人[2]、真女神[3]<br />\n出生 1986年7月6日（34歲）<br />\n 英屬香港<br />\n最高學歷 香港浸會大學傳理學（廣播新聞）榮譽社會科學學士<br />\n婚姻狀況 未婚<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%88%A9%E5%90%9B%E9%9B%85\" data-s